dex_entry: Its nose is trained in a way that makes it find solutions to any clues. Sadly they cannot convey this to humans.

name: Guard Dog
dex_entry: Known to guard mansions, houses and temples alike. But their barks bring terror to the neighboors.

name: Lycurgus
dex_entry: After the untimely death of Cerberus the original temple guardian. Lycurgus was put in to guard Paterdomus.

name: Yak Moorrissey Form
dex_entry: Warped by the powers of the abyss this species of yak serves powers unknown.

name: Yak Robin Form
dex_entry: Celebrating the festivities of wintuber this yak appears when the mood is jolly.

name: Yak Yaktrick Form
dex_entry: Adept at stargazing and an expert in cosmic arts these yaks carry telescopes to further their research.

name: Cabbage Sister Form
dex_entry: Member of Saint Elsebeth Citharade. This sister has taken the vow of silence for Saradoming.

name: Cabbage Crispy Form
dex_entry: A cabbage with a hat.

name: Strykewyrm Mini Form
dex_entry: Since theyre practicly defenceless they prefer to stay underground for most of the day.

name: Crocodile Normal Form
dex_entry: They mostly stand still near water holes waiting for prey to come to them.

name: Crocodile Mutadile Form
dex_entry: A very big crocodile lurking the chambers of Xerosic. It is a very good boy.

name: Crocodile Ankh Form
dex_entry: The magisters experimentation with souls caused this crocodile to gain power in trade for its will.

name: Crocodile Ukunduka Form
dex_entry: The curse placed on Crondis taken physical forme. It caused a vain and gluttoneous feeling in Crondis.

name: Bloodveld Insatiable Mutated Form
dex_entry: These demons once served Zaros but seemed to have gone over to Zamorak by the rebellion.

name: Bloodveld Acidic Form
dex_entry: The highly acidic fluids in its body makes them more dangereous than any other bloodsucker.

name: Bloodveld Vampiric Form
dex_entry: Mainly used as pets by Vyrewatch these bloodvelds stand guards in houses of Darkmeyer.

name: Bloodveld RS3 Form
dex_entry: CUPHOLDER

name: Beaver
dex_entry: They use their prolonged fangs to gnaw trees and build dams to live in.

name: Giant Beaver
dex_entry: Bigger than its regular counterpart these beavers could eat an entire magic tree.

name: Racoon
dex_entry: Known as 'washbears' to some these woodland critters love to eat garbage.

name: Ralph
dex_entry: In their sack they keep the loot they have stolen. They dont trust anyone to see whats in there however.

name: Rocky
dex_entry: These buggers sneak into adventurers bags to steal from them, but usually ends up as their pets.

name: Honey Badger
dex_entry: Known to not care for anything because its strong, ferocious and badass in every way.

name: Squirrel Giant Form
dex_entry: Bigger than regular squirrels these critters are acrobatic despite their larger shape.

name: Squirrel Australian Form
dex_entry: Antipodean squirrels are heralds of the Queen of Sunrise. Mostly to argue over the seasons.

name: Jade Vine
dex_entry: Related tot he strange plant these plants will grown violent if not pruned occasionally.

name: Klik
dex_entry: The dragonkins experimentation on dragons caused them to make a breed mixed of Dragon and Fairy.

name: Jackalope
dex_entry: A magical bunny growing horns, they are rare and elusive for people to see.

name: Imp
dex_entry: Known as a fire imp, these are the weakest demons that exist and love to play tricks on adventurers.

name: Demon Lesser RS3 Form
dex_entry: A Byzroth demon. Once slaves in their home realm. Now they fight for the god of chaos.

name: Demon Greater RS3 Form
dex_entry: An Alyaroth demon. Once used as slaves to the Chthonians, they now spread their wings for Zamorak.

name: Demon Kalgerion Form
dex_entry: One of the strongest demons summoned by Bilrach for his lord. Zamorak used them as generals in his army.

name: Demon Thundereous Form
dex_entry: Punished for his arrogance this demon got sealed away in the depths of Daemonheim.

name: Demon Ripper Form
dex_entry: They posess humans warping their appearence to slaughter everyone nearby.

name: Demon Lesser OSRS Form
dex_entry: Hailing from Infernus these Avernic demons were once a slave caste.

name: Demon Greater OSRS Form
dex_entry: Theyre called greater demons due to their wings and larger power, but so is their cruelty.

name: Demon Tstanon Form
dex_entry: Said to at one point have destroyed over 1000 planes this demon rains thunder on its enemies.

name: Demon Tormented Form
dex_entry: Their flesh burns as theyre fused with the draconic metal around them.

name: Delrith
dex_entry: A demon once sealed by the ancestor of todays Sir Prysin.

name: Demon Lesser Tongue Form
dex_entry: Their tongue is a source of pride since they have smaller horns than other demons.

name: Demon Greater Tongue Form
dex_entry: A great tongue is a sign of nobility in Infernus. But some claim its to excuse their rather small horns.

name: Demon Zakln Form
dex_entry: Known to some as Scourge of the light. Mostly because hailstorm and ice magic clouds the sky near its appearence.

name: Demon Pummeler Form
dex_entry: Carrying two large hammers this Kalgerion demon is so strong it can bash the fabric of planes.

name: Demon Chocolate Form
dex_entry: Made entirely of chocolate this demon runs into danger of eating its own delicious skin at times.

name: Demon Lesser Black Form
dex_entry: Black demons posess stronger power than their red counterparts but turns out to be equally cruel to others.

name: Demon Greater Black Form
dex_entry: Known for their strong black colour these demons are cruel and strong.

name: Demon Balfrug Form
dex_entry: Most known as the despoiler of Ullek. It shoots fireballs on anything they can see.

name: Demon Jungle Form
dex_entry: A poisoneous demon once summoned by gnomes to ambush a adventurer.

name: Demon Riftsplitter Form
dex_entry: With immense control of the planes around it this Kalgerion demon breaks the fabric of space at will.

name: Snow Imp
dex_entry: They help out Santa Claus in his workshop with a smile on their face.

name: Demon Ice OSRS Form
dex_entry: Despite not being physically made of ice the temperature around it grows so cold it might as well be.

name: Demon Ice RS3 Form
dex_entry: They can only live where its cold, and has since only been found in Ghorrock.

name: Demon Bloodchiller Form
dex_entry: Cotrolling immence power over coldness it gets its name from chilling a mans blood to solid ice.

name: Demon Reanimated Form
